title: Tin Foil Hat #43: UFOs and the Grinning Man Swapcast with The Grimerica Show
description:
Thanks for tuning into another crazy episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode, Ryan and Sam welcome Darren and Graham from the Grimerica Show podcast! On this show we discuss....
1) The Tin Foil Hat Comedy Show and Swapcast with the Higherside Chats' Greg Carlwood Oct 10th live at the Ice House Comedy Club. Tickets are available at IceHouseComedy.com!
2) The Grimerica Show
3) Synchronicity
4) UFO sighting and NBE's
5) Black Ops
6) Indrid Cold the Grinning Man
7) We read your iTunes reviews
If you would like to support the show you can make a donation on PayPal at TinFoilHatpod@gmail.com! We have big plans and we thank you for your support!
